---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
Page: 74
By: Sultan Bahu
---
I found God when I found love,
and it is this love that gives me strength
from one day to the next.
Love shows me the path I must take.

I am on fire
and I am the fuel that feeds the fire
and the smoke that rises from the fire.
Love made me aware of the Beloved.
